f=Engineering/ops/custom/release-discipline/assets/deploy-checklist.md · h1:Deploy Checklist — ops/release-discipline=Run order, deploy including hotfixes. Host-specific mechanics come business's platform-playbook; steps invariant. · h2:Preconditions=quinn GATE PASS reference attached (quality verdict), open rail violation; deploy plan LOCKED (plan id: ___) (security verdict), Change scope matches locked plan (no drive-by inclusions) · h2:Rollback (before deploying blocking)=Rollback path identified: previous artifact down-script feature-flag-off, Rollback EXERCISED staging (evidence: ___), Data compatibility confirmed (schema N-1 tolerance migrations involved) · h2:Migrations (if any Rail=dana's prepared script plain-language effect summary attached, OPERATOR ran (never agent, never auto-run pipeline), Sequenced expand migrate contract; deploy independently rollback-able · h2:Deploy=Strategy chosen playbook risk: blue-green canary rolling (recorded), Deploy window sane (someone watching; config `deploy_windows` set), Executed playbook §___ · h2:Verify (any failure ROLL BACK NOW, diagnose after)=Health checks green, Error rate latency within maintenance-hygiene baselines, Smoke critical flows (config `critical_flows`) passes, Watch window held (config `deploy_watch_window`): ___ CLOSED ROLLED BACK · h2:Record=Deploy record written (skill Output Format); rollbacks failures incident-response user-facing